<% layout('./layouts/boilerplate') -%>

<div class="container py-5">
  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome to <strong>Scribo</strong>! This platform is designed to bring together passionate writers, readers, and creators in a seamless, engaging, and interactive environment.
  </p>

  <h3 class="mt-4">Our Mission</h3>
  <p>
    Our mission is to provide a platform where users can create, share, and explore high-quality content. We aim to empower writers and make content easily accessible for readers around the world.
  </p>

  <h3 class="mt-4">Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Create, edit, and delete posts with rich content (HTML & Markdown supported)</li>
    <li>Upload cover images for posts, with default images if none are provided</li>
    <li>Like and unlike posts with real-time updates</li>
    <li>Comment system to interact with posts</li>
    <li>Tagging system to categorize posts</li>
    <li>Optional categories for better organization</li>
    <li>User authentication and authorization using JWT</li>
    <li>Flash messages for better user feedback</li>
    <li>Responsive and modern UI built with Bootstrap</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="mt-4">Technologies Used</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js</li>
    <li><strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB, Mongoose</li>
    <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> EJS, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap</li>
    <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> JWT, bcrypt</li>
    <li><strong>File Handling:</strong> Multer for image uploads</li>
    <li><strong>Version Control:</strong> Git & GitHub</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="mt-4">Our Vision</h3>
  <p>
    We envision a community where knowledge, creativity, and ideas can flow freely. Our platform is continuously evolving with new features to enhance user experience and engagement.
  </p>

  <h3 class="mt-4">Contact Us</h3>
  <p>
    If you have any questions, feedback, or suggestions, feel free to reach out via our contact form or email us at <strong>support@ourblog.com</strong>.
  </p>
</div>
